---
import Icon from '@/shared/components/Icon.astro'
---

<section class='problem' id='problem'>
  <div class='wrapper'>
    <div class='problem-header' data-aos='fade-up'>
      <span class='problem-label'>El problema</span>
      <h2 class='problem-title'>
        ¿Tu WhatsApp es un <span>caos</span> de preguntas y PDFs?
      </h2>
      <p class='problem-subtitle'>
        Si te identificas con alguno de estos problemas, no estás solo. Le pasa al 90% de los
        negocios que venden por WhatsApp.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class='problem-cards'>
      <div class='problem-card' data-aos='fade-up' data-aos-delay='100'>
        <div class='problem-card-icon'><Icon name='document-text' size={40} /></div>
        <div class='problem-card-content'>
          <h3 class='problem-card-title'>PDFs que nadie abre</h3>
          <p class='problem-card-text'>
            Clientes que abandonan porque el PDF no carga, es muy pesado o simplemente no lo quieren
            descargar. <strong>Perdiste la venta.</strong>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class='problem-card-indicator'></div>
      </div>

      <div class='problem-card' data-aos='fade-up' data-aos-delay='200'>
        <div class='problem-card-icon'><Icon name='arrow-path' size={40} /></div>
        <div class='problem-card-content'>
          <h3 class='problem-card-title'>Preguntas repetitivas</h3>
          <p class='problem-card-text'>
            Pierdes horas respondiendo <strong>"¿Qué precio tiene?"</strong> una y otra vez. Tiempo que
            podrías dedicarle a hacer crecer tu negocio.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class='problem-card-indicator'></div>
      </div>

      <div class='problem-card' data-aos='fade-up' data-aos-delay='300'>
        <div class='problem-card-icon'><Icon name='x-circle' size={40} /></div>
        <div class='problem-card-content'>
          <h3 class='problem-card-title'>Pedidos con errores</h3>
          <p class='problem-card-text'>
            Pedidos que llegan incompletos, con errores o confusos. Tú tienes que adivinar qué
            quería el cliente. <strong>Eso te cuesta dinero.</strong>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class='problem-card-indicator'></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .problem {
    position: relative;
    padding: 6rem 1rem;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--neutral-02) 0%, #f5f0f0 100%);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .problem-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto 3.5rem;
  }

  .problem-label {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.3rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2);
    color: #ef4444;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .problem-title {
    font-size: var(--48-pt);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--shade-03);
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .problem-title span {
    color: #ef4444;
    position: relative;
  }

  .problem-title span::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    bottom: 2px;
    width: 100%;
    height: 6px;
    background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2);
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .problem-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--shade-04);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .problem-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 72rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .problem-card {
    position: relative;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    transition:
      transform 0.3s ease,
      box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .problem-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-6px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

  .problem-card-indicator {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ef4444, #f97316);
    border-radius: 4px 4px 0 0;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
  }

  .problem-card:hover .problem-card-indicator {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .problem-card-icon {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.06);
  }

  .problem-card-title {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--shade-03);
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
  }

  .problem-card-text {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--shade-04);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 1024px) {
    .problem-cards {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      max-width: 500px;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
    .problem {
      padding: 4rem 1rem;
    }

    .problem-title {
      font-size: var(--40-pt);
    }

    .problem-subtitle {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .problem-card {
      padding: 1.5rem 1.25rem;
    }
  }
</style>
